You're updating your blog every week. You're sharing on every social media channel anyone might possibly be using. You've even shelled out for a website that's as beautiful as the pieces you're trying to sell.

But they're still not finding you.

Fortunately, there's one marketing trick you might not even know you have up your sleeve: the power of social connection. As an artist, you're in the perfect spot to build a brand based on this principle (and use it to make a living doing what you love best).

My new video course is designed to help you stand out even in the most crowded creative niche. Read on and check out the video clips below for a look at what I'll teach you.
